  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:0",
      "text": "无论你使用 online material library 中的 PBR maps，还是使用 Substance Painter 这类 texturing software，RenderMan 都附带了一个方便的 node，名为",
      "ascii_letters": 74,
      "cjk_chars": 24
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:1",
      "text": "PxrMetallicWorkflow",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:2",
      "text": "，它可以很方便地与 PBR maps 和 Lama workflow 配合使用。",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:4",
      "text": "本课使用的 maps 由我们的 rendering friends 提供，来自",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:5",
      "text": "Greyscalegorilla",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:6",
      "text": "，示例使用的是 Copper Corroded Heavy 01。",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:7",
      "text": "由于 Eagle model 没有任何 UVs，我们采用 triplanar approach，通过以下节点把 textures 映射到 model 上：",
      "ascii_letters": 43,
      "cjk_chars": 21
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:8",
      "text": "PxrMultiTexture",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:11",
      "text": "PxrTexture",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:12",
      "text": "node，而不是 PxrMultiTexture node。",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0ee8ae399b:13",
      "text": "Note: 目前，从 Substance Painter export Lama material network 时，需要更新 normal connections。你可以在 DCC 的 RenderMan menu 中选择 Update Lama Nodes，轻松完成这一步。",
      "ascii_letters": 93,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    }
  ],
